        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Certificate of scholarship and conduct for Stephen F. Austin.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            


<p>This certifies that the bearer <persName>Stephen F. Austin</persName> has been a <persName>member
of this <placeName>Institution</placeName></persName> and a <persName>Boarder </persName>in my family, most of the time, for
Three Years past. As a <persName>Scholar </persName>he has been obedient and studious;
as a <persName>boarder</persName>, unexceptionable. Having passed acceptably the public
examinations, and having during the whole period sustained a good
MORAL character, he is judged worthy of this honorary testimonial.</p>

<p>By order of the <persName>Trustees </persName>in such cases, provided.</p>

<p>attest <persName>John Adams Precepr</persName>    [Rubric]</p>
<p><placeName>Colchester Bacon Acady</placeName></p>

<p>Jany 7th 1808</p>

        </div1>
